en_Desc=Wild Wolves prowl our lands under the shadow of a sick moon. The weapons master summons you: you must not only hunt them, but also pluck from one of them its Cursed Fang. Only a wolf, touched by darkness, bears it. Seek, wait
en_DescFinal=You've done it! That tusk isn't obtained without courage. Take it to Bertrand, the famous Blacksmith of Nix; he may have a weapon for you.
